data.description: Don't let the current interest rates stop you from purchasing this beautiful home! There are many options available to help buy down the rate so you can own this well maintained all-brick ranch with NO HOA! This property features many updates including a new deck (2023), new roof (2021), new hot water heater (2021), and new flooring and paint (2023). HVAC was replaced in 2019. This home is located on over 1/2 acre conveniently located to downtown Greenfield and offers an open concept kitchen/dining room adjacent to a spacious living room. Cozy up next to the wood-burning stove during the winter months and enjoy the summer evenings on the wooden deck admiring the meticulously designed landscaping. Don't need 4 bedrooms? The extra large fourth bedroom in this home would serve as a great bonus room which would allow for two separate living spaces! This is a must see!
